。沒有人知道2047年的中國會不會因為有第二個像毛澤東一樣的政治人材，推動各省份改組成聯省政府，甚至成為獨立的不同省份共和國。沒有人是來自未來的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">，所以我仍然主張於2047年以公投形式，將合符當時《基本法》的所有選項列出，全民投票，決定香港前途。</span></span>"},{"pid":"01f1cca3a83bc29ce2943a10ade007da4b15542f","tid":1962282,"uid":121131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:32:10.000Z","msg":"唔好怪樓主啦 其實佢仲係小學生黎 <br />\n我係佢表哥 唔係好親個隻 <br />\n佢有少少低智個d唔好講啦 <br />\n佢讀特殊學校個d都無謂提 <br />\n不過大家放過佢啦 佢仲係讀緊小三 <br />\n佢老豆老母都好辛苦 要照顧樓主 <br />\n佢細細個已經食雞唔食雞皮 食橙食埋橙皮 <br />\n我代佢係呢度向大家道歉一聲"},{"pid":"1f6396f5443ca53c7b0f281481db07aa7c03b2dc","tid":1962282,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"咁唔係點呀！？講支持港獨，直接DQ！？"},{"pid":"77a141b314efea0eca0044476736aa82d66efaab","tid":1962282,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NV4L6yQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNV4L6yQ.png&h=607204e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7efa4d2e8234ea5886a32f2616cc8e05c328bb9","tid":1962282,"uid":274531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:32:50.000Z","msg":"樓主一係冇睇內容 一係有心分化<br />\n睇下篇文先啦屌"},{"pid":"4bf48536ebf77636833cbc2f888a21c6c015c2f5","tid":1962282,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:32:51.000Z","msg":"哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc4a23d8c6f4ddd9db161eeb8c216ff22bf7cfc","tid":1962282,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f09adaa5c7e5028ae63db11e533008e9106d0dc5","tid":1962282,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae598baee5719daa443ff8c95f26118015e888c8","tid":1962282,"uid":310571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"琴日睇立場見到：作為香港特別行政區第六屆區議員，本人乃真誠擁護基本法，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不